    "biography": "<p>A type of ancient cattle bred for the sport of long-dead nobility, a razorhorn is an aurochs-sized brute with steel horns that naturally hone to a superbly keen edge. Razorhorns breed slowly and are solitary in nature, but their tough hide and savage disposition make them dangerous even alone. Razorhorn flesh is remarkably delicious, and some lords require a tribute of it from villages located near razorhorn ranges.</p>"
